reviewText: Great job by the NFL including highlights of Super Bowls I and II, and of the 1966 and '67 playoff games against Dallas. The second disc includes highlights of the Super Bowl season when , led by Brett Favre, Green Bay beat New England for their third Super Bowl, completing the package.
Title: NFL Super Bowl Collection - Green Bay Packers

reviewText: incomplete is how i would describe it. i was expecting it to have more information about the games and the actual super bowl games.
